The paper deals with object detection using a fully convolutional neural network, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). The application domain is underwater robotics, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). The use of neural networks for object detection is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of proposals algorithms, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR).
